//!
//@Module NDIMS Number of Dimensions in Array
//@@Section Array
//@@Usage
//The @|ndims| function returns the number of dimensions
//allocated in an array.  The general syntax for its
//use is
//@[
//  n = ndims(x)
//@]
//and is equivalent to @|length(size(x))|.
//!
function n = ndims(x)
n = length(size(x));
